name: _unsorted
description: Default component for submitters, who do not know which component is responsible for the issue. Being sorted eventually (commonly once per week), quick response is not guaranteed.

name: analysis-core-plugin
description: Static Analysis Utilities - base functionality for all Jenkins' static analysis plug-ins

name: analysis-model
description: Static Analysis Model and Parsers - required by warnings-plugin and analysis-core-plugin

name: pipeline
description: A generic component for Pipeline issues. Use it when you do not know to which component the issue belongs

name: windows-slave-installer-module
description: Core module, which manages Windows agent service installation procedure. Also contains Jenkins-internal WinSW issues
